1
00:00:26,000 --> 00:00:32,000
秋风萧萧绕古城
Autumn wind whistles 'round the ancient town

2
00:00:32,000 --> 00:00:38,000
茶馆巷陌 说书的人
In teahouses and lanes, the storyteller sits

3
00:00:38,000 --> 00:00:44,000
街角掩庭院深深
Deep courtyards hide 'neath street corners

4
00:00:44,000 --> 00:00:50,000
藏燕青门里几度春秋
Within Yanqing Gate, years come and go

5
00:00:50,000 --> 00:00:54,000
雨打磨剑痕
Rain polishes the sword's scars

6
00:00:54,000 --> 00:00:58,000
武医心法贯乾坤
Martial and medical wisdom run through heaven and earth

7
00:00:58,000 --> 00:01:03,000
他抛洒的热血仍残留温存
The blood he shed still holds a trace of warmth

8
00:01:03,000 --> 00:01:09,000
曾有故事中的他
Once there was him in tales

9
00:01:09,000 --> 00:01:16,000
义薄云天 风姿潇洒
Righteous above all, graceful and unrestrained

10
00:01:16,000 --> 00:01:22,000
燕青引箭生繁花
Yanqing draws the bow, and flowers bloom

11
00:01:22,000 --> 00:01:29,000
扶危救困名震天下
Aiding the needy, his fame resounds across the land

12
00:01:29,000 --> 00:01:33,000
何以为侠
What is chivalry?

13
00:01:33,000 --> 00:01:38,000
耳畔风声无涯
The wind whispers endlessly by the ear

14
00:01:38,000 --> 00:01:43,000
可寻得真英雄的回答
Can we find the answer of a true hero?

15
00:01:43,000 --> 00:01:49,000
燕青门前十载春夏
Ten springs and autumns before Yanqing Gate

16
00:01:49,000 --> 00:01:55,000
武医天术纵横天下
Martial and medical arts prevail across the land

17
00:01:55,000 --> 00:02:06,000
为天地 为苍生 为国为家
For heaven and earth, for all living beings, for country and home

18
00:02:06,000 --> 00:02:10,000
我愿用我弹指剑花
I'd gladly use the sword flowers from my flick of the wrist

19
00:02:10,000 --> 00:02:14,000
挽出一个盛世繁华
To weave a prosperous age of glory

20
00:02:14,000 --> 00:02:17,000
再许你白首韶华
And vow to share with you the years till white hair comes

21
00:02:17,000 --> 00:02:32,000
啊 啊 啊
Ah, ah, ah

22
00:02:32,000 --> 00:02:36,000
星河欲转夜未休
Stars are about to shift, the night lingers on

23
00:02:36,000 --> 00:02:40,000
山河浩浩 天地悠悠
Rivers and mountains stretch vast, heaven and earth are boundless

24
00:02:40,000 --> 00:02:44,000
潮水自翻腾不休
The tide surges and rolls without cease

25
00:02:44,000 --> 00:02:49,000
似燕青门里侠义千秋
Like the eternal chivalry within Yanqing Gate

26
00:02:49,000 --> 00:02:53,000
风云几度
Through countless winds and clouds

27
00:02:53,000 --> 00:02:58,000
多少英雄风流
How many heroes lived in glory

28
00:02:58,000 --> 00:03:03,000
史册间 一抹英魂不朽
Between history's pages, a heroic soul remains eternal

29
00:03:03,000 --> 00:03:07,000
燕青门前十载春夏
Ten springs and autumns before Yanqing Gate

30
00:03:07,000 --> 00:03:11,000
武医天术纵横天下
Martial and medical arts prevail across the land

31
00:03:11,000 --> 00:03:15,000
为天地 为苍生 为国为家
For heaven and earth, for all living beings, for country and home

32
00:03:15,000 --> 00:03:20,000
我愿用我弹指剑花
I'd gladly use the sword flowers from my flick of the wrist

33
00:03:20,000 --> 00:03:24,000
挽出一个盛世繁华
To weave a prosperous age of glory

34
00:03:24,000 --> 00:03:28,000
再许你白首韶华
And vow to share with you the years till white hair comes

35
00:03:28,000 --> 00:03:34,000
如今你我盛世为家
Now we have this prosperous age as our home

36
00:03:34,000 --> 00:03:40,000
不见昔日金戈铁马
No longer seeing the old days of swords and armor

37
00:03:40,000 --> 00:03:47,000
名与利 功与禄 何足记挂
Fame and fortune, merits and ranks—what's there to care for?

38
00:03:47,000 --> 00:03:54,000
抛却俗世扰扰纷杂
Cast aside the chaos and noise of the mortal world

39
00:03:54,000 --> 00:04:08,000
明朝打马 仗剑天涯
Tomorrow we ride horses, wield swords across the land

40
00:04:08,000 --> 00:04:22,360
共并肩 逐梦天下
Side by side, chasing dreams across the land
